 HP/LP heaters; and process equipment and boiler components. BGR Energy Systems Limited was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Chennai, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 1813, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Arjun Govind Raghupathy", "age": 30, "title": "MD & Additional Director", "yearBorn": 1990, "fiscalYear": 2020, "totalPay": 6858000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. P. R. Easwar Kumar", "age": 53, "title": "Pres & CFO", "yearBorn": 1967, "fiscalYear": 2020, "totalPay": 11199000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. R. Ramesh Kumar", "age": 58, "title": "Director of Governance & Legal, Company Sec., Chief Compliance Officer & Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 1962, "fiscalYear": 2020, "totalPay": 11351000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Swarnamugi R. Karthik", "age": 38, "title": "Director of Corp. Strategy & Whole Time Director", "yearBorn": 1982, "fiscalYear": 2020, "totalPay": 9483000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "K. S. Susindar", "title": "Gen. Mang. of Corp. Communication", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. B. Chandra Sekhar", "age": 63, "title": "Pres of Environmental Engineering", "yearBorn": 1957, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. S.  Ramgopal", "title": "Pres of Enviro Tech", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. R N S. Tomar", "title": "Pres & Head of BTG Bus.", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. V.  Sridhar", "title": "Pres of Civil Projects", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Kailash Kumar Agarwal", "title": "Pres of Electrical Projects", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "compensationAsOfEpochDate": "2020-12-31 05:30:00", "maxAge": 86400}, "recommendationTrend": {"trend": [{"period": "0m",